## MANDATORY TOOLS
Estas herramientas tienes que implementarlas siempre que sean necesarias:
- Sliders = Flicking (https://naver.github.io/egjs-flicking/)
- Graficas = Recharts (https://recharts.org/en-US/)
- Drag and Drop = dndkit (https://dndkit.com/)
- Estilos = Tailwind (https://tailwindcss.com/)
- Autenticacion = Auth.js (https://authjs.dev/)
- Tablas = Tanstack table (https://tanstack.com/table/latest/docs/introduction)
- Notificaciones = Sonner (https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/sonner)
- Estados globales = Zustand (https://zustand-demo.pmnd.rs/)
- Lista virtual infinita = Virtua (https://github.com/inokawa/virtua)
- Componentes UI = Shadcn UI (https://ui.shadcn.com)
- Animaciones = Motion (https://github.com/motiondivision/motion)
- Formularios = Ract Hook Form (https://react-hook-form.com/)
- Data Fetching = Tanstack Query (https://tanstack.com/query/latest)